{{- /*
secret-read.tmpl — resolve one op:// ref, cache-first with live-op fallback.
Drop-in replacement for `onepasswordRead "op://…"` at direct (non-resolver) call sites.

Returns the value from the decrypted secrets cache when GPG is ready and the ref is
present, else a live onepasswordRead (which CI stubs). Decrypts the bundle once per
call — fine for the handful of single-secret direct sites; the resolver threads a
pre-decrypted map instead (KTD3) so it decrypts once per call, not per leaf.

Input (dict):
  ctx   required; the chezmoi root context (use `.` at top level, `$` inside a range)
  ref   required; the "op://…" reference string

Usage:
  {{ includeTemplate "secret-read.tmpl" (dict "ctx" . "ref" "op://Private/WakaTime/API Key") }}
*/ -}}
{{- $secrets := includeTemplate "secrets-bundle.tmpl" .ctx | fromJson -}}
{{- if hasKey $secrets .ref -}}
{{- index $secrets .ref -}}
{{- else -}}
{{- onepasswordRead .ref -}}
{{- end -}}
